name: underworld_selene
description:
my second TI: Selene from Underworld! trained on 40 images with 4000 steps! It´s trained on the complete character, not just the face, there where closeup images and full body shots in the training data

as with my other TI, add ((((beautiful face)))), ((perfect face)) to your prompt, just for safety ;)

the TI tends to latexclothing, of course because of the catsuit the character is wearing in the movie :D

modelVersions.name: V2.0
modelVersions.description: retrained on a smaller set of images without any background editing, so there shouldn´t be no more noise background as with the V1.0 I believe it gives better results with the original outfit, maybe just my feeling though
